data.description: Beautiful Ranch in a quiet cul-da-sac!!! Come in and make yourself at home. This 3 bedroom and 3 full bath home has everything you could want. Walking in the front door you are greeted with natural light pouring in from the large windows and sun room. The kitchen boasts an island, plenty of counter space, breakfast nook and a large pantry! Opening up the both the oversized living room and the dining room, you won't feel cramped for space. The owner's suite is situated off to itself with a HUGE walk in closet. Secondary bedrooms each have their own full bathroom and deep closets. Enjoy the open sunroom all year long that overlooks a private patio! Schedule your private tour today!
